Puzzle Game

Mechanichs:
Colored Keys to Open doors
Moving Boulders
Buttons to move blocks
Need to Get to an exit to complete level
Moving enemey blocks which can kill player

What we need:

__Collision__
On collision with key, a key is picked up and colorKey boolean is changed to true
On collision with a key door, if colorKey is true, door removed
When collided with a button, receiving object activates
When in contact with a boulder, if keyPress in the direction, boulder moves
If boulder collided with a button, receiving object activates
